WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Angolos' is a Workbench game played on an hexagonal-shaped
board, the idea is to link all the tiles on the board and return
to the starting tile and by doing so, make the biggest number of
angles (links that are not at 180 degres from one to another).

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-The game board can be resized and the game displays the biggest
 number of angles made for each board size.

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 doesn't take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

